INSERT INTO `recipedates` VALUES ('15', '10', '1', '1996-11-02', 'Brewed', '1.047', '0.0', 'Mash in at 114F for 15 mins. Boost to 122F for 20 mins. Pull 1/2grains raise to 158F for 15 mins and then boil for 30 mins.  Addback to main mash and raise to 15?F for 50 mins. Mash out at 168F.Boiled over and lost a bit to the ground. I don\'t know if hopsblewout or not, so I added another 1/4 oz and boiled for an hour. Chilled and pitched yeast. Temp @ 65F. Next morning got nice krausen. 11/5 krausen reached airlock and oozed out. Kewl.||11/7 took a hyrdo sample and drank it before I took the reading.It\'s good. Something went wrong. I didn\'t like and dumped it.');
