INSERT INTO `recipedates` VALUES ('94', '53', '1', '1999-10-23', 'Brewed', '1.095', '0.0', 'mash in @ 151F. Drop to 145F over 40 mins. Boost to 151F. Drop to148F over 20 mins. Boost to 158F. Rest for 15 mins. Boost to 168F. Batch sparge. Drain 1/2 & add more water. Recirc for a long time. Boil the wort for about an hour while recirculating. Drain the wort to kettle and boil for 1 more hour. Chill to 68F & pitch yeast. Transfer at 66F.|10/24 - 24 hours and yeast head just starting to rise.|11/5 - SG @ 1040 temp been about 62F.|12/1 - SG @ 1034 temp been in the low 60\'s.|3/1 - SG @ 1018 been in dining roomnext to rad pipes. Added champagne yeast some time ago. I guessit did its job.||Crisp Marris Otter base malt');
