INSERT INTO `recipedates` VALUES ('307', '172', '1', '2011-02-27', 'Brewed', '0.000', '0.0', 'North Star IPA (the homebrew recipe that became Sculpin). I\'ll leave cleaning up the formatting as an exercise for the brewer.||Hops|Amount Name Form Alpha IBU Boil Time|1.00 oz. Amarillo Gold Pellet 9.40 45.6 Mash H|0.50 oz. Warrior Pellet 16.30 35.9 60 min.|0.25 oz. Magnum Pellet 14.40 15.9 60 min.|0.25 oz. Hallertau Northern Brewer Pellet 7.10 7.8 60 min.|0.25 oz. Tomahawk, F-10 Variety Pellet 16.40 18.1 60 min.|0.25 oz. Crystal Pellet 3.60 2.0 30min.|0.25 oz. Centennial Pellet 9.90 5.6 30 min.|0.25 oz. SimcoePellet 13.60 7.6 30 min.|1.00 oz. Amarillo Gold Pellet 9.40 0.0 0min.|1.00 oz. Simcoe Pellet 13.60 0.0 Dry Hop|2.00 oz. AmarilloGold Pellet 9.40 0.0 Dry Hop||Extras|Amount Name Type Time|1.00 Unit(s) Whirlfloc Tablets Fining 15 Min.(boil)||Yeast|White Labs WLP001 California Ale');
